tns:TableColumns.tns:ColumnName: CASE WHEN MIS_DASHBOARD_JOBS.PROCESS_DATE > NOW() THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END
CASE WHEN ASCII(MIS_DASHBOARD_JOBS.ERROR) = 46 THEN 'N' WHEN LENGTH(MIS_DASHBOARD_JOBS.ERROR) > 0 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'DK' END
CASE WHEN HOUR(MIS_DASHBOARD_JOBS.PROCESS_DATE) = 0 THEN 24 ELSE HOUR(MIS_DASHBOARD_JOBS.PROCESS_DATE) END
CASE WHEN TO_CHAR(MIS_DASHBOARD_JOBS.START_DATE_TIME, 'DD-MM-YYYY') = TO_CHAR(CURDATE(), 'DD-MM-YYYY') THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END
CASE WHEN MIS_DASHBOARD_JOBS.ITEM_TYPE_ID = 0.00 THEN 'KPI' WHEN MIS_DASHBOARD_JOBS.ITEM_TYPE_ID = 1.00 THEN 'Chart' ELSE 'Unknown' END
CASE WHEN MIS_DASHBOARD_JOBS.STATUS = 'C' THEN 'Complete' WHEN MIS_DASHBOARD_JOBS.STATUS = 'W' THEN 'Waiting' ELSE 'Cancelled' END

tns:Tables.tns:TableName: (SELECT MIS_COLUMNS.SERIAL,MIS_COLUMNS.DISPLAY_NAME FROM PUBLIC.MIS_COLUMNS MIS_COLUMNS UNION ALL SELECT MIS_DEFINED_CHARTS.SERIAL,MIS_DEFINED_CHARTS.DESCRIPTION FROM PUBLIC.MIS_DEFINED_CHARTS)
